name: San Mateo County Health
tweet: There are NO walk-up or additional appointments at the Playland vaccination clinic for kids aged 5-11 at the San Mateo County Event Center. Anything you see on social media about appointments being available is false. People arriving without appointments will be turned away.

name: San Mateo County Health
tweet: Kids appointments (5-11) at the Event Center Playland clinic are full for Saturday 11/6. The number of doses available for Saturday is limited; families without appointments will not be able to get their children vaccinated. Please don’t come to Playland without an appointment.
